	<chapter id="user-manual">
		<title>User Manual</title>
		<section>
			<title>Activate Code Recommenders for your projects</title>
			<para>
				Code Recommenders Intelligent Code Completion features are not enabled per default. You need to activate them
				explicitly for your project by adding the Recommenders Nature to the project. To enable Code Recommenders, either:
				<mediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="media/figures/completion/enable-via-completion.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</mediaobject>
				or:
				<mediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="media/figures/completion/enable-via-context-menu.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</mediaobject>
			</para>
		</section>
